OL,3,CPredatory former postman jailed for
OL,4,Cseries of sex offences
OL,6,FA predatory former postman has been
OL,7,Fjailed following a series of sex
OL,8,Foffences in Northumberland.
OL,10,FMichael Stewart abused his position to
OL,11,Ftarget five women, with his offending
OL,12,Fcoming to light after one of his
OL,13,Fvictims came forward to police in
OL,14,FNovember 2021.
OL,16,FStewart, 63, of Windsor Terrace,
OL,17,FAmble, was arrested, and later charged
OL,18,Fwith 10 counts of sexual assault,
OL,19,Fthree counts of exposure and one count
OL,20,Fof harassment with fear of violence.
