OL,3,CPredatory former postman jailed for
OL,4,Cseries of sex offences
OL,6,FHe denied the offences but was found
OL,7,Fguilty on eight counts of sexual
OL,8,Fassault and all other charges
OL,9,Ffollowing a nine-day trial at
OL,10,FNewcastle Crown Court in November last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FStewart appeared before the same court
OL,14,Fon Wednesday (19 February) where he
OL,15,Fwas sentenced to six years and six
OL,16,Fmonths behind bars.
OL,18,FHe will also spend the rest of his
OL,19,Flife on the Sex Offenders' Register.
