OL,6,FLeading the investigation, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Anthony Gourley, of
OL,8,FNorthumbria Police, said: "Michael
OL,9,FStewart is a calculating and dangerous
OL,10,Fpredator who abused his position to
OL,11,Ftarget his victims and subject them to
OL,12,Ftraumatic ordeals.
OL,14,F"He has been brought to justice thanks
OL,15,Fto the extraordinary strength and
OL,16,Fbravery of those abused to come
OL,17,Fforward and report the offences.
OL,19,F"Tragically, two of his victims died
OL,20,Fbefore seeing Stewart convicted and
OL,21,Fsentenced."
