OL,6,FDet Con Gourley added: "We are
OL,7,Fcommitted to supporting all victims of
OL,8,Fsexual offences ` and putting
OL,9,Foffenders before the courts.
OL,11,F"I would urge anyone who has been a
OL,12,Fvictim ` regardless of when the
OL,13,Foffences took place ` to come forward.
OL,15,F"Our message is clear ` we are here
OL,16,Ffor you."
