OL,6,FAnyone who has been the victim of any
OL,7,Fform of sexual abuse ` whether recent
OL,8,For non-recent ` can contact police
OL,9,Fusing the 'Report' pages of the
OL,10,FNorthumbria Police website, by using
OL,11,Fthe Live Chat function on the website,
OL,12,For by sending a direct message on
OL,13,Fsocial media.
OL,15,FFor those unable to contact police
OL,16,Fthis way, call 101.
OL,18,FAlways call 999 in an emergency.
